And that just feels like what all of everything is made up of and we're all stuff making more stuff and other stuff. And stuff can get you down or it can make you laugh and stuff is kind of what it's all about, a big song and dance of stuff! Yet that's not quite as true as I'd like it to be, because there's some really nasty bad bad stuff out there, and it's that kinda stuff that makes other stuff seem pointless at times.
